<i>adverb</i>: 하긴 [하긴], 하기는 [하기는], 즉 [즉], 이야말로 [이야말로], 그야말로 [그야말로], 과연 [과연], 가히 [가ː히], 가위 [가ː위] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>하긴 [하긴]</dt><br>
<dd>in fact; in truth; indeed; actually</dd><br>
<dd>사실 말하자면.</dd><br>
<dd>To tell the truth.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>하기는 [하기는]</dt><br>
<dd>in fact; in truth; indeed; actually</dd><br>
<dd>사실 말하자면.</dd><br>
<dd>To tell the truth.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>즉 [즉]</dt><br>
<dd>1. that is</dd><br>
<dd>다시 말하면, 바꾸어 말하면.</dd><br>
<dd>In other words or to put it another way.</dd><br>
<dd>2. indeed</dd><br>
<dd>바로 다름 아닌.</dd><br>
<dd>No less than.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>이야말로 [이야말로]</dt><br>
<dd>just; indeed</dd><br>
<dd>(강조하는 말로) 앞의 이야기가 바로.</dd><br>
<dd>(emphasizing form) Just the thing mentioned in the preceding sentence.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>그야말로 [그야말로]</dt><br>
<dd>certainly; indeed; really</dd><br>
<dd>(강조하는 말로) 사실 그대로.</dd><br>
<dd>(emphasizing form) Truly.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>과연 [과연]</dt><br>
<dd>1. indeed</dd><br>
<dd>생각대로 정말로.</dd><br>
<dd>Exactly as expected.</dd><br>
<dd>2. indeed</dd><br>
<dd>결과에 있어서도 참으로.</dd><br>
<dd>Without question about expected results.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>가히 [가ː히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. well</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 일에 뛰어나게. 또는 어떤 일에 넉넉하게.</dd><br>
<dd>Excellently in something; or sufficiently in something.</dd><br>
<dd>2. indeed</dd><br>
<dd>아닌 게 아니라 정말로. 또는 어떤 경우에도 절대로.</dd><br>
<dd>Really, or surely in any case.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>가위 [가ː위]</dt><br>
<dd>indeed</dd><br>
<dd>말하자면 정말로.</dd><br>
<dd>Really, so to speak.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>